00:04:08.239 --> 00:04:11.560
more reasons why to stick to a healthier diet.

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:17.650
And especially finding reasons that help you
day in and day out constantly remind yourself

00:04:17.650 --> 00:04:19.239
why you want to make these changes.

